**Bug report 5\. \- Benefiti responsive**

**Title/Summary:** The Layout is not responsive on mobile.  
**Description:** Accessing [https://demo.benefiti.rs/?\#/](https://demo.benefiti.rs/?#/) on a mobile device reveals usability issues due to a non-optimised responsive design for small screens (see images below).

.![][image1] ![][image2]

**Environment:** Mobile phone (Samsung A54 5G), Android 14, OneUI 6.1, Google Chrome app version: 136

**Steps to Reproduce:**	

1. Go to [**https://demo.benefiti.rs/?\#/**](https://demo.benefiti.rs/?#/).

**Expected Results:** The layout should adapt to mobile screen size. All navigation and content should be accessible without zooming or horizontal scrolling..

**Actual Results:** The left navigation panel is zoomed in and overflows. The user must manually zoom out or pan to interact with key elements..

**Severity: High**

**Priority: Medium**
